document_data.mainbody:
Holyhead was a small coastal village located in the kingdom of Callidyrr on the island of Alaron within the Moonshae Isles.
Holyhead was found in northern Callidyrr in the county of Stagford on Alarons eastern coast with the Sea of Moonshae. The village sate just west of the ominous Dernall Forest and north of the Drowned Forest.
